#### {% label info@ES6%}  - 解構賦值 Destructuring assignment
可以把陣列或物件中的資料解開擷取成為獨立變數
詳細請見:[MDN-解構賦值](https://developer.mozilla.org/zh-TW/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Operators/Destructuring_assignment)

```js
const o = {p: 42, q: true};
const {p, q} = o;

console.log(p); // 42
console.log(q); // true

///
const o = {p: 42, q: true};
const {p: foo, q: bar} = o;

console.log(foo); // 42
console.log(bar); // true
  ```





